This template generates an external link an author's page at the [[Microsoft Academic Search]] website.

== Usage ==
: <code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}} | ''ID'' }}</code>
: <code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}} | id= ''ID'' }}</code>

